409 U.S. 921 93 S. Ct. 1350 35 L. Ed. 2d 583 In the Matter of the Disbarment of Seymour R. THALER. No. D-9. Supreme Court of the United States February 20, 1973
11 It is ordered that Seymour R. Thaler of New York, New York, be suspended from the practice of law in this Court and that a rule issue returnable within forty days requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
